name: Misato Katsuragi - Neon Genesis Evangelion
description:
Surprisingly there was no LORA here for Misato. So I made one. I also like Rei, but only on Mogudan style, I'll probably make that LORA at some point.

Had nice results with: <lora:Katsuragi_Misato:.45>, Katsuragi_Misato, big_breasts, cross_necklace

The Lora turned out fine, I made an effort to try to add her "scar" but that went a bit iffy. It does show in the correct location, but not the stitches. Be careful of not setting it's value too high or it gets weird.

According to the tags summary other useful ones could be the following:

  • scar

  • jewelry

  • earrings

  • jacket

  • cross

  • red_jacket

  • necklace

  • bangs

  • cross_necklace
